#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:5
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//ship[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "那艘船四分五裂，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:8
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//ship[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:13
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//ship[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "敌方船员尽数死亡，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:16
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//ship[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:23
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS_FIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"星之子已然覆灭，外部的巨大团块似乎也平静了下来——它那巨型触须选择不再纠缠你的"
"飞船，重新收缩回本体。你不禁好奇星之子究竟是如何操控它的，又或者这根本不是它"
"的运作方式……无论答案如何，你总算成功避免动用火焰之力。但愿手握此物，再加上些"
"许运气，你能完成任务：抵达这地狱之地的核心，将物质病毒彻底根除。查看地图，该"
"区域的奇异信号在出口处最为密集……那里一定就是核心所在。现在，只剩下出发这一步"
"了……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:25
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "那么，前进——前往核心！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:35
msgid "data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你的飞船从虫洞的另一端被抛射出来，虫洞在你身后迅速闭合……你发现自己置身于一片"
"黑暗、宛如深渊般的宇宙空腔之中。外界的黑暗里没有一颗星辰闪烁；这里唯一的光亮"
"，来自远方一抹微弱而斑斓的光晕。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:45
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "这里……就是那座监狱吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:47
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"外界一丝极其微小的黑暗从它那无法估量的庞大本体中挣脱扭曲而出，你这才意识到，"
"这根本不是普通的黑暗……这整片地方，就是一个由灵魂瘟疫感染物质构成的、庞大得难"
"以想象的巨穴！这缕黑暗此刻已获得行动能力，正朝着你的飞船逼近，而异域的低语也"
"开始笼罩你的心神：\n"
"“……入侵者……来了……”\n"
"“……新鲜的血肉……加入我们……”\n"
"“……成为……家人……”\n"
"你拼命想要驱散这些念头，可它们却如同潮水般不断涌入。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:56
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你是什么东西？滚出我的脑袋！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:58
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"低语轻柔，语气近乎友善：\n"
"“……我们……是众子……”\n"
"“……星辰之子……”\n"
"“……星……星之子……”\n"
"它们的形态在你脑海中浮现：黑暗、不祥的甲壳族，身躯中央散发着虹彩光芒……尽管它"
"们的模样让你感到几分熟悉，却有种不安的预感——它们的心智，并不比你见过的那些灵"
"魂瘟疫躯壳更加充实。它们的目光，同样空洞无神。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:66
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "星之子……那位披甲的女士提到过你们。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:68
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"一提到她，那些声音立刻变得阴险又充满斥责：\n"
"“……那位女杰……卑劣至极……”\n"
"“……希望的棋子……可怕的存在……”\n"
"“……碎星者……凶手……”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:74
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我……我知道你们的把戏！你们骗不了我！滚开！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:76
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"即便你怒斥它们，低语却再度变得轻柔：\n"
"“……不必……如此急躁……”\n"
"“……前往核心……路途遥远……”\n"
"“……投入我们的怀抱……感受安宁……”\n"
"你感到手中那团金色火焰燃烧得愈发明亮；触上去依旧不烫。而你无比真切地发现，它"
"变得格外令人安心，就像脑海中那些声音刚刚所暗示的一样……这，就是它据说能揭示的"
"真相本质吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:84
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/text"
msgstr "（希望之焰）燃尽疑虑的阴影。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:86
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你握紧手中的火焰，外界那无边无际的灵魂瘟疫聚合体立刻做出了反应。一部分物质猛"
"地翻腾而起，狂怒地咆哮着冲向你的飞船，你脑海中的声音也在尖啸……可它们全都无能"
"为力。火焰的力量轰然爆发，化作一道从你的飞船向外迸发的光浪——一股无可匹敌的力"
"量，瞬间同时摧毁了那艘被灵魂瘟疫感染的诡异飞船，以及正朝你扑来的物质狂潮。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:91
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:93
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "一切平息之后，火焰为你揭示了一个真相……那便是慰藉。尽管你尚未理解，但你能感觉"
"到，这个真相可以化作任何你所期望的模样。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:96
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "我能想到的慰藉……就是把飞船修好。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:98
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"火焰释放出的残余能量仿佛凝聚成形，环绕在你的飞船四周。当这股力量渐渐消散时，"
"你惊讶地发现，船壳已经奇迹般地修复完毕……这东西究竟是什么？无论答案如何，你都"
"必须记住那位披甲女士的话：它的力量是有限的。但愿凭借它，再加上些许运气，你能"
"完成任务——抵达这片地狱之地的核心，将物质病毒彻底根除。查看地图，该区域的奇异"
"信号在出口处最为密集……那里一定就是核心所在。现在，只剩下出发了……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:101
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "那么，前进——前往核心！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:107
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我能得到的慰藉……就是补充燃料。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:109
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
