#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4006
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "它最后的守护者倒下，灵魂瘟疫吞噬者发出凄厉的嘶吼——随后它的力量耗尽，开始逐渐"
"枯萎。这头巨兽，已然倒下！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4011
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4018
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_NOTALLHOPEISLOST\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"战斗愈演愈烈，你本以为核心体将会对你的舰船发动攻击……可相反，你脑海边缘再次传"
"来微弱的低语：\n"
"\n"
"“……不……不要再受苦了……”\n"
"“……这场疯狂……就到此为止……”\n"
"“……就算我……必须与它一同死去……”\n"
"\n"
"战场之外，核心体的心脏光芒愈发炽亮，它那无数狰狞的触手在剧烈痉挛中停下了逼近"
"的动作……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4026
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_NOTALLHOPEISLOST\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4028
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_NOTALLHOPEISLOST\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……可他们仿佛被一股全新的信念所支配，将所有怒火都对准了灵魂瘟疫吞噬者！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4036
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_NOTALLHOPEISLOST\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "所有人，继续保持压制！我们能做到的！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4044
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr "守护者已被击败，核心心脏暴露在外……现在只剩下终结这一切。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4050
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "寻找曾协助过你的那位女杰。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4052
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr "你在货舱里找到了她，她正刺向一具残存的空壳傀儡。你走近时，她转过身看向你：“同"
"志！结束了吗？核心心脏已经暴露了？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4055
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "已经暴露了。我们接下来该怎么做？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4057
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"她示意你跟上来，然后带你返回驾驶舱。窗外的光芒依旧那般美好……你感觉它又在对你"
"低语：\n"
"\n"
"“……你做到了……你赢了？”\n"
"“……我从不敢……确信这会成为可能……”\n"
"“……这真的……是结局了吗……？”\n"
"\n"
"那位身披铠甲的女性注意到你心神不宁，歪了歪头：“出什么事了吗？如果没有，我想我"
"们是时候终结这一切了。它的守护者已被击败，只需一记强力的攻击摧毁核心心脏，就"
"能彻底结束这场噩梦……别担心！我可以在这里安全地发动攻击。这便是英雄之希望的力"
"量……”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4066
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我想……那颗心脏在和我说话。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4068
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"毫无疑问，它是在绝境中用虚假的承诺引诱你。别理会它，同志；若是形势逆转，它会"
"毫不犹豫地将你毁灭。那么，如果你没有异议的话……” 她握紧手中的长矛，数个与她一"
"模一样的单色分身出现在心脏外的空间中。她们蓄势待发，而你不禁思索……她曾提及英"
"雄希望的力量。如果那颗心脏真的在与你对话，或许有办法能毫无悬念地揭露它的真实"
"意图……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4070
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/text"
msgstr "（希望之焰）燃尽疑虑的阴影。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4072
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你不知为何，却感到一股力量驱使你握住先前得到的那簇火焰残烬。当你握住它时，火"
"焰熄灭，一股能量浪潮向外扩散，那位铠甲女子也停下了攻击。火焰的能量汇聚在核心"
"体心脏周围，在它四周形成了一道屏障……突然间，屏障消散，心脏那发光的外壳开始……"
"裂开。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4075
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "敬畏地凝视着。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4077
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"如今愈发明亮的光束从心脏的外壳中迸发而出，它的裂痕不断扩大，显露了内部的景象…"
"…一具甲壳族躯体，其光芒棱镜般的绚烂程度甚至远超星之子。它瘫软无力的身躯从破碎"
"的心脏残骸中滑落，开始毫无生气地漂浮在宇宙中……就在这时，外部的核心体开始发出"
"尖啸，剧烈震颤——这个地方正在分崩离析！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4081
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "抓住那个甲壳族！我们快做好防护！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4083
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你下达指令，那位身披铠甲的女子点了点头：“我……从不知道这座监牢的核心竟然是一个"
"人。看来这些墙壁藏着不少秘密，不过……别担心！我能把他们带进去！”她的分身们接住"
"那道身影，你操控飞船前去接应，而你周围的核心体正在迅速崩解……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4085
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4087
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……时空碎裂，核心体的额外维度被撕裂，露出了底下那片熟悉的星空。你……成功了！你"
"摧毁了核心体！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4091
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "看向那名身披铠甲的身影，还有那具奇异的甲壳族躯体。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4093
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你从不会过早欢庆，转头看向他们两人。她正蹲伏在倒地的甲壳族身旁，似乎在施展着"
"什么手段……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4095
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "让她按自己的方式做吧。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4097
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你自然认为她是行家。你敢肯定，在这片时间凝滞、仿若度过数百年的孤寂之地，她早"
"已无数次练习过复苏之术……还没等你意识到这话听上去有多残酷，一道熟悉的金光骤然"
"迸发，她一掌击在甲壳族身上，厉声喝道：“活过来，该死的！你不能死在这里——绝不能"
"在我眼皮底下死去！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4099
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你确定那是……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4101
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的话被硬生生打断，那具甲壳族猛地向前一倾，咳出数团已经失去活性的灵魂瘟疫感"
"染物质。她向后退了退，给对方留出空间，他看向你们两人，虚弱地咕哝道：“其……其他"
"人……你们……”他被迫再次咳嗽，打断了话语，在身旁的地面上弄出一片狼藉。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4103
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "其他人？你指的是谁？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4105
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "“我……我的下属。他们……他们一直和我一起被困在核心体里。他们……还在吗？他们还好吗"
"？”他说的一定是星之子……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4107
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "嗯……我想他们已经不复存在了。恐怕物质病毒已经把他们彻底侵蚀了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4109
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他闻言又剧烈咳嗽起来，随后仰面躺倒，望着天花板：“天啊……都怪我。我怎么会这么愚"
"蠢……为什么偏偏是他们？为什么不干脆把我带走？这……这是对我的惩罚吗？难道我要永"
"远独自在这里腐烂，为我的过错赎罪吗……？”他看起来有些神志不清……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4111
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你到底是谁？还有……你到底做了什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4113
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他重新转向你，你发现他开始……悬浮在半空中，开口说道：“我……我是……等等，我为什么"
"想不起自己的名字？它连这个也夺走了吗？！你不可能……天啊，为什么？”他的声音近乎"
"哽咽，晃了晃神，又试着回答你的问题：“我……大概就像我刚才说的，哈……‘愚蠢至极’。"
"至于我做过什么……我该从何说起？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4115
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "不如从头说起？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4117
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“好，好吧。那……首先，我——天啊，我曾经是怪才体政府的首席科学家之一，负责科学区"
"的艾普西隆实验室。我们当时在研究如何创造出完美的劳动力——一种我们能够掌控、可"
"以执行任何任务的存在。不过在实现方式上存在分歧——阿尔科莱打算取代管理区，就像"
"他之前掌控军事区那样，但内尔瓦显然表示反对……我也是。我站在她这边，我和其他志"
"同道合的科学家来到这里，这样我们就能在不受阿尔科莱破坏性影响的情况下继续研究"
"。”甲壳族顿了顿，再次抬起头：“那就是……一切出错的开始。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4119
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "发生了什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4121
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他叹了口气：“首先——他或许残暴成性，但阿尔科莱绝对是个天才。没有他的协助，我们"
"这边的研究进展慢得如同爬行。物资供应又是另一个难题；我们再也无法依靠行政区的"
"资金了。然而，最终真正致命的一击……是那件该死的神器。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4123
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "神器？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4125
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"我……我甚至都不知道它到底是什么，可它一直在对我们低语。对我。承诺会修复一切，"
"让我们完成研究……随着情况越来越糟，我们很清楚，在完成项目之前，我们就会在这里"
"发疯，我……我达成了一笔交易。我做了交易，结果却害了所有人……天啊……”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4127
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你到底……和谁做了交易？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4129
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他转向你，甲壳之中散发出恐惧的气息：“即便到现在，我也说不出口。他们在我的梦里"
"现身，向我许下同样的承诺……我只记得远处那阵该死的、地狱般的机械转动声。我崩溃"
"了，对未来充满担忧，它问我最想要什么……我能想到的只有完成项目。在那之后，我……"
"我就再也没有从那场梦里醒来。”他环顾四周，摸了摸自己的双手，“我想，直到现在才"
"醒过来，可是……天啊，它把他们全都夺走了，不是吗？所有信任我的人……就连我们的研"
"究成果也被夺走，扭曲成了这……这些……这些怪物！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4131
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你是指物质病毒吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4133
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“那……他们是这么叫它的吗？我们本想做些好事，为了所有人的福祉，结果却被扭曲成了"
"可怕的宇宙腐化者……而我……我也是其中一部分。我能感受到它所感受的一切；它对星辰"
"的憎恨，对生灵的憎恨，对时间本身的憎恨……它只想吞噬一切。”他微微下沉，身体轻轻"
"弹离地面，又开始喃喃自语，“我们……我们本来是想帮助别人的……我到底做了什么……现在"
"只剩我一个人了，我还……我还糟蹋了他们所有的心血……”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4135
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4149
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "其实你不必解释，我已经知道了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4151
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他蜷缩起身体：“那……你知道真相了，对不对？我们本来……我们本来是想帮助别人的，而"
"我……天啊，我到底做了什么……我现在孤身一人，还……还把他们的心血彻底毁了……”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4153
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4179
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "保持安静。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4189
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "寻找曾协助过你的那位女杰。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4196
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_HEROINEENDING\"]/text"
msgstr "所有分身一同攻向核心，核心瞬间碎裂——碎片朝着四面八方飞散。随着核心被摧毁，外"
"部的核心体开始发出尖啸，剧烈震颤——这个地方正在分崩离析！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4199
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_HEROINEENDING\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "做好准备！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4201
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_HEROINEENDING\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你寻找掩护，却几乎找不到，但事实证明这毫无必要，因为你周围的核心体正在迅速瓦"
"解……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4203
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_HEROINEENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4205
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_HEROINEENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "随着时空碎裂、核心体的额外维度被彻底撕裂，底下那片熟悉的星辰景象显露出来。你…"
"…成功了！你摧毁了核心体！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4209
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_HEROINEENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "太棒了！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4211
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_HEROINEENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这位身披铠甲的女子拍了拍你，力道之大让你不由得后退，她开口道：“同志，就得这么"
"干！不过……我有种感觉，物质病毒的残余势力，依然散落在多元宇宙的各个角落。嗯……"
"那就这么定了！继续前进，并肩作战——踏上属于英雄的征途！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4213
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_HEROINEENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "等等，什么？你要留下来？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4215
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_HEROINEENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"她大笑起来：“你在跟我开玩笑吗？我被困了……天啊，鬼知道到底多久了，我还有好多混"
"蛋等着去收拾呢。你知不知道，年复一年、日复一日、一遍又一遍地打那些黏糊糊的怪"
"物，到底有多无聊？！更何况——你和我并肩作战，一同挺身而出，只因为这是正确的事"
"。我们是同志！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4217
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_HEROINEENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "好吧，呃！那行！那你愿意介绍一下自己吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4219
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_HEROINEENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "一声巨响，她将矛柄重重砸在地面，摆出战姿：“我，乃是女中豪杰！族人的救星，恶徒"
"的克星——传说本身！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4221
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_HEROINEENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "好吧……那，你的族人到底是谁？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4223
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_HEROINEENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"她收起姿势，歪了歪头：“你不认识深渊潜者吗？还是说……是因为这副铠甲？我现在想想"
"，确实很难看出来……算了，不管了！重点是——我们现在是同志了！出发！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4225
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_HEROINEENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "前进！为了多元宇宙！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4227
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_HEROINEENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你们两人短暂地庆祝了一番，随后四周归于平静，启程离开的时刻终究还是到来了。你"
"在这片炼狱的旅程，就此落幕……但全新的征途与际遇，仍在前方静候着你。究竟会是怎"
"样的未来……谁又能知晓呢？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4246
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/text"
msgstr "遗憾的是，她似乎在战斗中牺牲了……但至少你能完成她未竟的事业。你感觉，这一定也"
"是她所希望的……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4249
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "攻向核心。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4251
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你也怀着沉重的心情，转身面对核心体的心脏。外面的光芒依旧如此绚烂……你感觉它又"
"在对你低语：\n"
"\n"
"“……你做到了……你赢了吗？”\n"
"“……我从……不敢相信这是可能的……”\n"
"“……这……这真的是……结束了吗……？”\n"
"\n"
"即便到了现在，它还在试图引诱你吗？如果它真的在与你对话，一定有办法能毫无疑问"
"地揭露它真正的意图……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4260
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/text"
msgstr "（希望之焰）燃尽疑虑的阴影。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4262
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你不知道为什么，却感觉自己不由自主地握住了先前得到的那簇火焰残烬。就在你握住"
"的瞬间，火焰熄灭，一股能量浪潮向外席卷而去。火焰的能量在核心体的心脏周围汇聚"
"，在它四周形成了一道屏障……突然间，屏障消散，心脏那发光的外壳开始……碎裂。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4265
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "敬畏地凝视着。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4267
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"心脏的裂缝不断扩大，更加耀眼的光束从其表面迸发而出，展露了内部的景象……一具甲"
"壳族躯体，其绚烂棱镜般的光芒甚至远超星辰之子。它瘫软的身躯从破碎的心脏中滑落"
"，毫无生机地漂浮在宇宙中……就在此时，外界的核心体开始发出尖啸，剧烈震颤——这片"
"空间正在崩解！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4271
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "抓住那个甲壳族！我们快做好防护！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4273
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "尽管这是一次冒险的操作，你还是驾驶飞船飞过去接住了那具甲壳族躯体，而你周围的"
"核心体正在迅速崩解……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4275
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4277
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "随着时空碎裂、核心体的额外维度被彻底撕裂，底下那片熟悉的星辰景象显露出来。你…"
"…成功了！你摧毁了核心体！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4281
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "照料这具奇异的甲壳族躯体。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4283
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你从不会过早欢庆，立刻跑到你救回的那具甲壳族躯体旁。尽管它看上去已被物质病毒"
"彻底侵蚀，但你绝不会因此放弃拯救它……它似乎没有呼吸，可触碰时仍带着温度，身体"
"还在微微搏动。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4285
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "试着摇晃它。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4287
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这算不上最聪明的办法，却是个还算稳妥的初步选择。但令你震惊的是，这居然奏效了"
"；那具甲壳族躯体猛地向前一倾，咳出数团已经失活、被灵魂瘟疫感染的物质。你后退"
"几步，给它留出一些空间，它看向你，虚弱地咕哝道：“其……其他人……你是否……” 话音未"
"落，它又被迫咳嗽起来，在身旁的地面上弄得一片狼藉。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4289
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "其他人？你指的是谁？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4291
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "“我……我的部下。他们……他们一直和我一起被困在核心体里面。他们……还在吗？他们还好"
"吗？” 他说的一定是星之子……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4293
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "好吧……我恐怕他们已经什么都不剩了。物质病毒应该已经把他们彻底侵蚀了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4295
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他听后咳得更厉害了，随后仰面躺倒看向天花板：“天啊……该死。我怎么会这么蠢……为什"
"么偏偏是他们？为什么带走的不是我？这……这是对我的惩罚吗？难道我要永远独自在这"
"里腐烂，为我的过错赎罪……？”他看起来有些神志不清……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4297
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你到底是谁？还有……你到底做了什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4299
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他重新转向你，你发现他开始……悬浮在半空中，开口说道：“我……我是……等等，我为什么"
"想不起自己的名字？它连这个也夺走了吗？！你不可能……天啊，为什么？”他的声音近乎"
"哽咽，晃了晃神，又试着回答你的问题：“我……大概就像我刚才说的，哈……‘愚蠢至极’。"
"至于我做过什么……我该从何说起？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4301
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "不如从头说起？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4303
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“好，好吧。那……首先，我——天啊，我曾经是怪才体政府的首席科学家之一，负责科学区"
"的艾普西隆实验室。我们当时在研究如何创造出完美的劳动力——一种我们能够掌控、可"
"以执行任何任务的存在。不过在实现方式上存在分歧——阿尔科莱打算取代管理区，就像"
"他之前掌控军事区那样，但内尔瓦显然表示反对……我也是。我站在她这边，我和其他志"
"同道合的科学家来到这里，这样我们就能在不受阿尔科莱破坏性影响的情况下继续研究"
"。”甲壳族顿了顿，再次抬起头：“那就是……一切出错的开始。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4305
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "发生了什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4307
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他叹了口气：“首先——他或许残暴成性，但阿尔科莱绝对是个天才。没有他的协助，我们"
"这边的研究进展慢得如同爬行。物资供应又是另一个难题；我们再也无法依靠行政区的"
"资金了。然而，最终真正致命的一击……是那件该死的神器。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4309
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "神器？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4311
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“我……我甚至都不知道它到底是什么，可它一直在对我们低语。对我。承诺会修复一切，"
"让我们完成研究……随着情况越来越糟，我们很清楚，在完成项目之前，我们就会在这里"
"发疯，我……我达成了一笔交易。我做了交易，结果却害了所有人……天啊……”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4313
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你到底……和谁做了交易？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4315
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他转向你，甲壳之中散发出恐惧的气息：“即便到现在，我也说不出口。他们在我的梦里"
"现身，向我许下同样的承诺……我只记得远处那阵该死的、地狱般的机械转动声。我崩溃"
"了，对未来充满担忧，它问我最想要什么……我能想到的只有完成项目。在那之后，我……"
"我就再也没有从那场梦里醒来。”他环顾四周，摸了摸自己的双手，“我想，直到现在才"
"醒过来，可是……天啊，它把他们全都夺走了，不是吗？所有信任我的人……就连我们的研"
"究成果也被夺走，扭曲成了这……这些……这些怪物！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4317
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你是指物质病毒吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4319
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“那……他们是这么叫它的吗？我们本想做些好事，为了所有人的福祉，结果却被扭曲成了"
"可怕的宇宙腐化者……而我……我也是其中一部分。我能感受到它所感受的一切；它对星辰"
"的憎恨，对生灵的憎恨，对时间本身的憎恨……它只想吞噬一切。”他微微下沉，身体轻轻"
"弹离地面，又开始喃喃自语，“我们……我们本来是想帮助别人的……我到底做了什么……现在"
"只剩我一个人了，我还……我还糟蹋了他们所有的心血……”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4321
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4335
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "其实你不必解释，我已经知道了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4337
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他蜷缩起身体：“那……你知道真相了，对不对？我们本来……我们本来是想帮助别人的，而"
"我……天啊，我到底做了什么……我现在孤身一人，还……还把他们的心血彻底毁了……”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4339
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_hopesflamecharges\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4363
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "摧毁核心。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4365
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "你倾尽所有力量轰击核心，它轰然碎裂——碎片向四面八方飞散。随着核心被彻底摧毁，"
"外界的核心体开始发出尖啸，剧烈震颤——这个空间正在崩塌！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4368
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "做好准备！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4370
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你寻找掩护，却几乎找不到，但事实证明这毫无必要，因为你周围的核心体正在迅速瓦"
"解……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4372
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4374
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "随着时空碎裂、核心体的额外维度被彻底撕裂，底下那片熟悉的星辰景象显露出来。你…"
"…成功了！你摧毁了核心体！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4378
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "现在……该怎么办？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4380
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"尽管你取得了胜利，或许还将现实从物质病毒的肆虐中拯救了出来，你却丝毫没有胜利"
"者的感觉……当初是否有什么事你本可以换一种方式去做？你无从知晓，但你很清楚：这"
"里已经什么都不剩了。是时候继续前行了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4394
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING_PARTTWO\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"就在你试图寻找合适的话语时，甲壳族摇了摇头，然后重新看向你：“他们……他们的名字"
"！我想起来了！阿斯贝卡尔、努尔里克、格加思……没错，我都记得！”他的声音里再次燃"
"起了希望，因为他意识到并非一切都已逝去，“我至少能做的，就是以他们的名义活下去"
"，尽我所能纠正这一切。我……我仍然能感受到物质病毒的影响。就算你已经解救了我，"
"摧毁了核心体，我还是担心它的其他菌株已经在别处滋生出了更小的聚合体……如果不会"
"成为你的负担，我想请求你，无论你去往何方，请让我跟随着你，或许我们可以……一起"
"，摧毁它们，好吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4396
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING_PARTTWO\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "如果你打算先去收拾那些叛军，那我奉陪到底！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4398
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "甲壳族闻言兴奋地上下浮动：“你说的是叛军叛乱？也难怪，我半休眠了近千年，他们居"
"然还在蹦跶……算我一个！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4401
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "愚者"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4403
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "太棒了！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4405
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_FOOLISHENDING_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你们两人短暂地庆祝了一番，随后四周归于平静，启程离开的时刻终究还是到来了。你"
"在这片炼狱的旅程，就此落幕……但全新的征途与际遇，仍在前方静候着你。究竟会是怎"
"样的未来……谁又能知晓呢？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4414
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_GREATESTENDING\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"就在你试图寻找合适的话语时，这位身披铠甲的身影站起身，她的护手再次按在自己心"
"口，另一只手指向甲壳族：“唯独你，还能记得你的族人——记得他们所付出的牺牲。或许"
"你觉得这是诅咒，但这其实是一份荣耀。你为他们的死自责，可扭曲你这份成果的并不"
"是你——那是某种古老、邪恶、远超你理解的存在所为。”她放下手，按在长矛上，“如果"
"你在这里沉溺于悲伤，就此放弃……还有谁能继承你逝去友人的遗志？还有谁能为他们复"
"仇，活着记住他们的名字？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4416
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_GREATESTENDING\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4418
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_GREATESTENDING\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"她的话语似乎触动了他，他稍稍振作了一些：“对……他们的……名字。我能记得他们！阿斯"
"贝卡尔、努尔里克、格加思……没错，我都记得！”他转向你，声音里带着希望：“我……我"
"仍然能感受到物质病毒的气息。就算你已经解救了我，摧毁了核心体，我还是担心它的"
"其他菌株已经在别处滋生出了更小的聚合体……如果不会成为你的负担，我想请求你，无"
"论你去往何方，请让我跟随着你，或许我们可以……一起，摧毁它们，好吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4420
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_GREATESTENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "如果你打算先去收拾那些叛军，那我奉陪到底！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4422
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_GREATESTENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "甲壳族闻言兴奋地上下浮动：“你说的是叛军叛乱？也难怪，我半休眠了近千年，他们居"
"然还在蹦跶……算我一个！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4425
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_GREATESTENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "愚者"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4427
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_GREATESTENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "太棒了！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4429
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_GREATESTENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "身披铠甲的女子闻言拍了拍甲壳族的后背，又拍向你，力道大得让你下意识一缩，她开"
"口道：“那就这么定了！一起出发——踏上属于英雄的征途！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4431
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_GREATESTENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "等等，你也一起来？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4433
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_GREATESTENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"她大笑起来：“你在跟我开玩笑吗？我被困了……天啊，鬼知道到底多久了，我还有好多混"
"蛋等着去收拾呢。你知不知道，年复一年、日复一日、一遍又一遍地打那些黏糊糊的怪"
"物，到底有多无聊？！更何况——你和我并肩作战，一同挺身而出，只因为这是正确的事"
"。我们是同志！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4435
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_GREATESTENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "好吧，呃！那行！那你愿意介绍一下自己吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4437
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_GREATESTENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "一声巨响，她将矛柄重重砸在地面，摆出战姿：“我，乃是女中豪杰！族人的救星，恶徒"
"的克星——传说本身！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4439
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_GREATESTENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "好吧……那，你的族人到底是谁？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4441
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_GREATESTENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"她收起姿势，歪了歪头：“你不认识深渊潜者吗？还是说……是因为这副盔甲？我现在想想"
"，确实很难认出来……算了，不管了！重点是——我们现在是战友了！出发！”愚者虽然被她"
"的活力弄得有些不知所措，还是努力跟上她的兴奋：“是、是……出发！为了……呃……多元宇"
"宙？！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4443
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_GREATESTENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "前进！为了多元宇宙！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4445
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_THEDEVOURER_WIN_GREATESTENDING\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你们三人短暂地欢庆了片刻，随后一切归于平静，离开此地的时刻终究还是到来了。你"
"在这片炼狱中的旅程就此落幕……但全新的征途与际遇，仍在前方等待着你。究竟会是怎"
"样的未来……谁又能知晓呢？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4465
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_VILLAINSLAYER\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "看来就连她也拦不住你！你觉得，要是你真的全力以赴，他能阻止你吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4468
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_VILLAINSLAYER\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4476
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_VILLAINSLAYER_CREWKILL\"]/text"
msgstr "看着不灭的烈焰从女杰的铠甲之下喷涌而出，一股灼烈的恨意撕扯着你的心脏……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4479
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_VILLAINSLAYER_CREWKILL\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4481
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_VILLAINSLAYER_CREWKILL\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"……而伴随着她，那些陨落的战友也与她一同苏醒。你压下心中的情绪，转而燃起属于你"
"自己的执念——那股要将他们全部再次斩杀、一遍又一遍、永不停歇的炽烈欲望……直到一"
"切化为虚无。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4489
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_VILLAINSLAYER_DEATHTOEVIL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"战斗愈演愈烈，你感觉到女杰再次在你脑海中嘶吼：“感受他们的痛苦——沉溺在他们的绝"
"望之中……去死吧，你这该死的东西！”她的舰船竟奇迹般开始再生，那些被你打入深渊的"
"灵魂仿佛在你四周升起……而你，似乎早已坦然迎接他们愤怒的撕扯。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4496
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_VILLAINSLAYER_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"…当你又一次战胜了一名所谓的英雄时，黑暗之神对你说道：“就连我，当年想要镇压此"
"人也颇为费力。那股无可比拟的执念……我的确羡慕你。”一道刺眼的光芒在房间中显现，"
"光芒散去后……你看见一柄前所未见的武器出现在面前。“这位女杰……已被我掌控。像你这"
"样的存在，我愿以你的名义将她重铸。去吧，随心所欲，做你想做的事。”你自然会这么"
"做。自你有记忆以来，你向来如此。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4504
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT_FIGHT_VILLAINSLAYER_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

