#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4547
msgid "data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/text"
msgstr "就是这里——灵魂瘟疫核心体的中心。你在这段旅程中一直看到的微弱光芒，此刻不再遥"
"远……这里一定就是它的心脏所在。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4555
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "真不敢相信我们居然做到了……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4557
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr "一路艰苦跋涉、浴血奋战，你感到筋疲力尽……但只剩下最后一件事要做。你很清楚自己"
"为何而来。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4559
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "继续深入。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4561
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你继续向前行进，寻找核心体的心脏，随即注意到远方有一物——那正是核心体光芒的源"
"头，一座绚烂无比、流光溢彩的中继器。它的模样绝美，近乎空灵，你不禁沉醉在震撼"
"之中，这时它向你轻声低语：\n"
"\n"
" “……这里……不安全……”\n"
"“……它在……狩猎你……”\n"
"“……你必须……离开，趁还来得及！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4568
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "蛤？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4570
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "这些低语与你一路上听到的截然不同；它们不再那么微弱，反而更显……急促吃力。可你"
"还没来得及根据这些警告做出反应，一道巨大的阴影便赫然浮现……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4572
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4574
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"……现身的是一艘被灵魂瘟疫感染的舰船，仅仅是它的体积就足以让你心生恐惧。更不用"
"说它那双巨大的眼眸，仿佛能刺穿你的灵魂、将你彻底看穿，还有它无数条不断扭动的"
"触须。这是贪婪与吞噬的化身……你惊恐地注视着它，新的低语正钻入你的脑海：\n"
"\n"
"“……沉溺……在我们的爱意之中……”\n"
"“……沉没……在我们的怀抱之中……”\n"
"“……我们会……为你的逝去而悲伤……”\n"
"\n"
"你的死期……这就是终点了吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4588
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/text"
msgstr "不，还不是时候……变元者，向来只由自己掌控命运。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4590
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你手中紧握的并非火焰，也不是武器，而是另一样东西……你的希望。你对存在的希冀，"
"对生命与光明未来的向往——这些信念在你心中熊熊燃烧，你感到，在外界那片浩瀚的光"
"与狂乱之海中，有一颗与你相通的灵魂正向你伸来援手……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4592
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/text"
msgstr "向它伸出手。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4594
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你无法解释这一切，但你还是伸出了手……有一只看不见的手紧紧握住了你。你用尽全身"
"力气向后拉扯，只见你的手周围裂开一道时空缝隙，并且不断扩大，一个熟悉的身影显"
"露出来——握住你的人正是早前遇见的那位铠甲女子！你继续发力，直到她从虫洞中挣脱"
"出来，重重跌落在地面上。她站起身，拂去身上被灵魂瘟疫沾染的物质，将护手按在胸"
"口，语气铿锵有力地说道：“真正的英雄，就是你，同志！我就知道，我对你的信任绝非"
"徒劳……”她顿了顿，望向外面那艘恐怖的舰船，随即又看向你，“……看来我来得还不算晚"
"。核心的守护者就在前方等候，你准备好了吗，同志？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4596
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "当然。我与你并肩作战。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4598
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"她点了点头，举起长矛：“我也与你同在！前进，现在就出发——荣耀在等待！为了希望，"
"为了多元宇宙！！！”她纵身向前，朝着舰船深处奔去，而你也做好了准备……就是此刻。"
"是时候证明你的信念，哪怕为此付出生命！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4602
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "女杰"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4604
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4620
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "终于……她来了吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4622
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"仿佛是在回应你疲惫的疑问，外界的虚空之中骤然爆发一道超新星般的强光……熟悉的黑"
"暗笼罩了这片空洞洞窟，一位女杰现身于此。她从一开始就必定看穿了你的恶行，故意"
"将你引到这里……这算不上什么英雄的手段。你能清晰感受到她的怒意，她仅凭意志便向"
"你开口：“别以为我不知道你是什么东西——你都做了些什么。我或许是这里的囚徒，但你"
"却更加卑贱：你是自身欲望的囚徒。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4628
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "那你又算什么？来教训我吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4630
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"她低吼道：“我是来阻止你的，恶魔！就连核心体都惧怕你……它愿意与我合作，给我自由"
"来到这里与你战斗，一切都是为了它自身的存续。只要能让你和你的恐怖统治就此覆灭"
"，我甘愿成为它计划中的一枚棋子。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4635
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "那就随你吧，不过……我想你会发现，你所做的一切都是徒劳。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4637
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"那就愚蠢地去死吧，在你那膨胀的自我中沉溺……因为我将全力以赴！在希望之刃下被碾"
"碎吧，恶人——尝尝你肆意施加于他人的痛苦！一声怒吼响起，她的舰船朝着你的方向冲"
"来……就是此刻。是时候终结这场闹剧了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4645
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4657
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "唉，一切都已不复存在。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:4659
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"DDCOREMASS_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_soulplague_coremass_heartdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr "的确，看来已经没有别的路了。你再次抵达了这段痛苦旅程的终点……这一次，你会走出"
"去吗？"
